      "title": "关闭非必要外联",
      "description": "一次性关闭自动更新、反馈命令、错误上报和遥测，适合对离线、隐私或网络稳定性要求更高的环境。",
      "doc_url": "https://code.claude.com/docs/en/env-vars",
      "patches": [
        {
          "target": "claude_settings",
          "path": "env.CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_NONESSENTIAL_TRAFFIC",
          "value": "1"
